{"tid":1167908,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因火山爆發而獲利 日本擴增領海及專屬經濟區","createTime":"2019-05-23T10:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T10:55:24.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"01683d7b172121c4804d765330e82e77e66f2700","tid":1167908,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpxOWhMr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpxOWhMr.jpg&h=8923a4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 日本西之島的面積因火山噴發而逐漸增大，使得日本的領海及專屬經濟區不斷擴大。（圖擷取自google衛星圖）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日本小笠原群島當中的西之島，自從2013年之後火山噴發不斷，熔岩造成島嶼面積不斷擴大，也使得日本再次擴增其領海及專屬經濟區（EEZ）的範圍。<br />\n<br />\n根據《共同網》報導，日本保安廳22日透露，西之島因火山噴發不斷，使得該島的面積不斷增加，日本將在31日修訂該島周邊的地形圖及海域圖，以擴增其領海及專屬經濟區。這次的修訂，將是日本繼2年前的修訂之後，再次擴增該島的領土範圍。<br />\n<br />\n在修訂之後，西之島的面積將增加0.17平方公里，達到2.89平方公里，海拔也增加17公尺，達到160公尺，領海擴大約4平方公里，專屬經濟區擴大約46平方公里。<br />\n<br />\n西之島乃是無人島，自從2013年發生近40年來首次噴發，以及後續的數次噴發之後，該島的面積原先0.29平方公里，在2017年時的修訂中增加9倍，擴增為2.72平方公里，此次將再往上修訂成2.89平方公里。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2799403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2799403&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo5AcLRrMd6FPy3rP8eGE4os%3D&h=98ff51a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2799403&h=610feb45\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2799403</a>"},{"pid":"b55cde32f607777de0165677002941dc2da0123d","tid":1167908,"uid":254183,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"支那拿人民納稅錢填海，日本免費造陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60132a5f76603011b4683ef42e4ab581cbf786d","tid":1167908,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:52:00.000Z","msg":"大日本帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d3fc02552c7e3fdfbbe81e1b245d5d4e552c68","tid":1167908,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好正"},{"pid":"70ab19eeb01472a8041ad5a6d99cee32b9f7065d","tid":1167908,"uid":218081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:55:24.000Z","msg":"以後可能會有人為火山爆發"}]}